t                       | px            | The height of the element                   | n/a\n text-decoration              | string        | underline/overline/line-through/none        | n/a\n text-transform               | string        | uppercase/lowercase/capitalize              | n/a\n align                        | string        | left/right/center/justify                   | left\n container-background-color   | color         | inner element background color              | n/a\n padding                      | px            | supports up to 4 parameters                 | 10px 25px\n padding-top                  | px            | top offset                                  | n/a\n padding-bottom               | px            | bottom offset                               | n/a\n padding-left                 | px            | left offset                                 | n/a\n padding-right                | px            | right offset                                | n/a\n css-class                    | string        | class name, added to the root HTML element created | n/a\n","readmeFilename":"README.md","_id":"mjml-text@4.0.0-beta.2","_npmVersion":"5.5.1","_nodeVersion":"9.1.0","_npmUser":{"name":"iryusa","email":"maxime.brazeilles@gmail.com"},"dist":{"integrity":"sha512-V9Ledf4YiHsxY37nf/cDKrauJJI2hxqE7BeYNw1t1ZhuEV0jlUewiN5cv+syVypuEtDQRbZAawoPkiCGAIipsA==","shasum":"6eea87024eb6937fa30cda5ae64eae5e5f68bbb1","tarball":"https://registry.npmjs.org/mjml-text/-/mjml-text-4.0.0-beta.2.tgz","fileCount":4,"unpackedSize":7415,"signatures":[{"keyid":"SHA256:jl3bwswu80PjjokCgh0o2w5c2U4LhQAE57gj9cz1kzA","sig":"MEYCIQDr0F90mNXngUkDvXEX5OlODbvi5c0DmigWXCXcMpGzOwIhAPpg/EW2Ow4P0553IrCDJe7Fkf6wVmxeZG2Z6Pmy1c5h"}]},"maintainers":[{"email":"maxime.brazeilles@gmail.com","name":"iryusa"},{"email":"loeck@mailjet.com","name":"loeck"},{"email":"meriadec.pillet@gmail.com","name":"meriadec"},{"email":"hi@mjml.io","name":"mjmlio"},{"email":"nicolas.garnier1@yahoo.fr","name":"ngarnie